{
  "_comment": "Merged model: full dry input, energy-active targets, tail+enthalpy weighting, sigma_floor 1e-10, head fine-tune. spectral_norm=false and consistency_weight=0.02 are MEASURED defaults (GPU A/B 2026-06-12: SN-on + cons 0.1 costs ~0.19 absorption R2 at k=16 and early-stops by epoch ~10; SN remains available as a CFD-stability ablation lever). rollout_mode=lagrangian assumes fine-dtau (front-adaptive) data - use manifold on stride-stored databases. Certification on HPC front-adaptive DB.",
